    dcterms:isPartOf <https://www.gov.uk/government> ;
    schema1:description "Andrew is a member of the senior leadership team in the Office of the Parliamentary Counsel (OPC) and is also the Second Parliamentary Counsel. Andrew is in charge of a team that delivers legislation for HMRC (eg, the Finance Bill following the budget) and the Treasury (eg, financial services) as well as DWP."@en ;
